      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I had to remove the &quot;.class&quot; in the command otherwise I got a message, &quot;Error: Cannot find foo.class&quot;. So doing, &quot;javap -verbose foo | grep &quot;major&quot;&quot; worked. Just a heads up. <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13356811/java-javap-errorcould-not-find-class\" title=\"java javap errorcould not find class\">stackoverflow.com/questions/13356811/&hellip;</a>"
