      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "As Jim advises, for vi addicts: &quot;vi MyClass&quot; then &quot;&lt;Esc&gt; :!xxd&quot; then peep at byte 8; 0x31, 0x32, 0x33, 0x34, 0x35 stands for java 5, 6, 7, 8, 9 respectively. &quot;&lt;Esc&gt; :q!&quot; to exit vi."
